column5: Good call, Ritchie...looks like a stocker to me.  Amazing fish, Raf...thanks for that!!  Drifter -- my heart skipped a few beats when you said Temagami!!
there she goes    hopefully that gives everyone the warm & fuzzies
Awwwww Raf.....that looked good for the smoker!!!!  Solid fish man!!
Beauty. You still gettin' them up top?  (Side note: wha happened to the Johnny Depp porn beard/stache?  )
Nice fish, love the colours.
The feelgood thread of the summer.  This should give the C&R Nazi's a wetness in they're drawers...
thanks for the warm and fuzzies
To steal a quote from that large gentleman on WFN:  "That excites me down to my googles"  Sweet fish for sure. Happen to get a tape on that beast?
Sleeping to close to the cat I'll bet.  Nice fish Raf.
probably!  stock photo  we've been in pike mode for a few weeks now   gives me a warm feeling all the time   approx 38"
hahaha Spiel.  you're good!!
Niiiiice fish Raf!!  Just wondering, after a fish like that I would be grinning from ear to ear, you almost seem disappointed in that pic. Give yourself a good pat on the back after that fish!
nice laker!
Maybe my buddy was in the next boat holding this guy up.
Judging by what you are wearing I would say that laker is pre-porn star look???
hearingfish i am surprised my eyes are even open  i don't photo well  drifter that's a hawg but i was on lake 'x' not 'gs' lake  john you are correct sir.  thought i'd lighten the mood.
Nicotine, valium, vicadin, marijuaner, extasy and alcohol...  OOOHHHHHHH!!!!!  Noice one brah!  teeehheeh HD
haha... great fish Raf.  I remember that day well.  Truly a hog and the biggest lake trout I've ever laid eyes on.
She's a brute for sure.  You're Gonna have to beat that measly 38" this year Raf  Joey
That's not GS Lake though. It was caught in Temagami!!!!  Well, er  not really it's a Great Bear Trout.
beauty fish man!
Thats the way Raf. Let the little ones go. Where's the picture of the bigger one you guys ate?
What a beast! Good job. Kenny G.
Big dark fat fish. That is a pig of a laker.
Pretty fishie. Interesting to note it doesn't seem to have an adipose fin. Stocker?
Congratulations on that monster, Rafal. What a beauty!
